sailpoint.tools.ldap

Class ObjectClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.ldap.ObjectClass

  • public class ObjectClass
extends java.lang.Object
    An ObjectClass represents an object class defined in an LDAP schema. Note that the attributes returned do not include attributes from parent object classes (for example - SUP). 
       RFC: http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2252.txt
